info.author: Hans Petter Langtangen, Alessandro Marin
info.name: DocOnce
info.summary: Markup language similar to Markdown targeting scientific reports, software documentation, books, blog posts, and slides. DocOnce can generate LaTeX, Sphinx, HTML, IPython notebooks, Markdown, MediaWiki, and other formats
